    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A naturalistic or geometricized motif derived from the species Dianthus caryophyllus, commonly used in Oriental carpets, especially in Turkey.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
